[32m│[0m 2. What database system is in use                                            [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m **Results indicate NO SQL injection vulnerability:**                         [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - All timing tests returned sub-millisecond responses (~0.001s)              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - If SQL injection worked, we'd see 5+ second delays                         [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - The application architecture doesn't use SQL at all                        [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
