[32m│[0m The application uses PHP serialized cookies instead of database queries. The [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m cookie `creds` contains:                                                     [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - Serialized PHP array format: `a:2:{...}`                                   [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - Direct storage of user input in the cookie                                 [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - No database interaction (evidenced by consistent fast response times)      [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
